524
01:09:28,525 --> 01:09:29,685
Su-yeon!

525
01:09:41,137 --> 01:09:42,297
Su-yeon!

526
01:09:46,509 --> 01:09:47,976
To není pravda, že ne?

527
01:09:48,611 --> 01:09:51,978
Je to pravda, tak odejdi!

528
01:09:52,916 --> 01:09:54,781
Odejdi pryč!

529
01:10:05,328 --> 01:10:06,795
Jestli neodejdeš,

530
01:10:08,431 --> 01:10:09,693
zabiju i sebe.

531
01:10:15,138 --> 01:10:17,868
Odejdi ! Jdi ode mě pryč!

532
01:10:38,828 --> 01:10:39,795
Su-yeon!

533
01:11:04,721 --> 01:11:05,688
Su-yeon!

534
01:11:08,124 --> 01:11:09,284
Su-yeon!

535
01:11:10,326 --> 01:11:13,591
Su-yeon! Su-yeon!

536
01:11:15,732 --> 01:11:19,998
Su-yeon, nechala jsem mobil..
Někdo doma?

537
01:11:20,737 --> 01:11:21,795
Su-yeon!

538
01:11:23,806 --> 01:11:27,765
Su-yeon! Co se stalo?

539
01:11:27,911 --> 01:11:30,573
Su-yeon! Su-yeon!

540
